<h2 id=3D"id-3.1.1Theoptions-Taggingdashboardsandfilteringbytag">Tagging da=
shboards and filtering by tag</h2>
<p>Tags are useful as they allow the user to assign identifyable terms (=3D=
 tags) to an item. The can then use any of those tags to find the item they=
 are looking for, or related items.</p>
<p>A downside is that they involve a lot of mental work from the user as it=
's not always easy to come up with a good tag name.</p>
<p>The system could attach predefined tags, such as the assetname/location/=
company.</p>
<p> </p>
